General.Name: Renewable Innovations Inc.
General.Description: Renewable Innovations, Inc., a hydrogen and fuel cell solutions provider, focuses on designing, optimizing, developing, and producing modular, scalable, and zero-carbon green renewable solutions in the United States and internationally. The company provides mobile and transportable HFC-powered EV rapid charge systems; hydrogen transport and refueling vehicles; and greenhouse grids to power communities. It serves government agencies and Fortune 500 companies. The company is based in Lindon, Utah.
